654
00:37:20 --> 00:37:26
so we have at the pin mg up.

655
00:37:22 --> 00:37:28
Sum of all forces is zero,
sum of all torques is zero.

656
00:37:26 --> 00:37:32
But there is a big difference

657
00:37:28 --> 00:37:34
between this situation
and this situation,

658
00:37:30 --> 00:37:36
